_sText:
I made this map because my friend Crazy[Virus] told me to try mapping.
I added around 62 spawns and buy zones, 32 spawns for each team.
There's a little bit of camping and barricading in this map.
Yet again a big thanks to Crazy for teaching me how to map.

So please leave some feed back, thanks. 


All prefabs from Fpsbanana, all the prefabs used were from Jking, ._:_ENEMY_:_. , and  Hamster.
